{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"write"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"buffer"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv","text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"!, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"count"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) "},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize","text":"gssize"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If count is 0, returns 0 and does nothing. A value of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"larger than "},{"code":"G_MAXSSIZE","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will cause a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"invalidArgument"},{"type":"text","text":" error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"On success, the number of bytes written to the stream is returned.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can happen e.g. on a partial I\/O error, or if there is not enough"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"storage in the stream. All writes block until at least one byte","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is written or an error occurs; 0 is never returned (unless"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" is 0)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", then the operation can be cancelled by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned. If an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"partial result will be returned, without an error.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"On error -1 is returned and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"type":"text","text":" is set accordingly."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedOutputStreamRef\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"write","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"buffer","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"count"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"text":"?) ","kind":"text"},